### Module 4: Trading Economy

**Learn**: HashMaps, file I/O, simple algorithms

**Build**: A dynamic market with prices that change based on supply/demand.

**Price Calculation**:

```java
public class Market {
    private Map<String, Double> basePrices;
    private Map<String, Integer> supply;
    private Map<String, Integer> demand;
    
    public double getPrice(String commodity) {
        double base = basePrices.get(commodity);
        int supplyLevel = supply.getOrDefault(commodity, 50);
        int demandLevel = demand.getOrDefault(commodity, 50);
        return base * (1 + (demandLevel - supplyLevel) / 100.0);
    }
    
    public void updatePrices() {
        // Simulate daily market changes
        Random rand = new Random();
        for (String commodity : basePrices.keySet()) {
            supply.put(commodity, supply.get(commodity) + rand.nextInt(10) - 5);
            demand.put(commodity, demand.get(commodity) + rand.nextInt(10) - 5);
        }
    }
}
```

