**Enemy AI**:

```java
public class EnemyShip {
    private double x, y;
    private double health;
    private double speed;
    private int aggression;  // 1-10
    
    public void update(PlayerShip player) {
        if (aggression > 5) {
            // Chase player
            double dx = player.x - x;
            double dy = player.y - y;
            double dist = Math.sqrt(dx*dx + dy*dy);
            if (dist > 100) {
                x += (dx/dist) * speed;
                y += (dy/dist) * speed;
            } else {
                // Attack
                fireAtPlayer();
            }
        } else {
            // Patrol randomly
            wander();
        }
    }
}
```

